To update slurm:
 1. pull latest tarball from schedmd.com or github.com
 2. untar into ../../../../build/ (BUILDWHERE)
 3. change generic "slurm" link to point to the untarred directory (ex. ln -s slurm-20.02.0 slurm)
 4. Copy tarball into the untarred directory (where the rpm slurm.spec file is located)
 5. If need be, adjust slurm.spec to match build options (debug, pmix, etc)
